{"tid":839650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[女權鬥士]唔妥自私精搭車擘髀坐？ 勇俄女用呢招KO佢哋","createTime":"2018-09-28T05:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T09:50:02.000Z","uid":25240,"like":8,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"842a978b01b4a98817a488eb4c99f52ca8f5bf0a","tid":839650,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"外國近年流行「男人擘腳坐」（manspreading）一詞，形容男性乘搭公共交通工具時張開雙腿而坐，甚至佔用了鄰座空間，毫不尊重他人。俄羅斯一名女大學生決定不再容忍，要「擘腳坐」的人有個深刻教訓－－她往對方的褲檔倒一些稀釋漂白水，聲稱要冷卻其「擘腳坐」意欲，亦令衣物留下永不磨滅的「印記」。<br />\n<br />\n20歲的法律系學生多夫加柳克（Anna Dovgalyuk）近日上載一段短片，<span style=\"color: red;\">她在聖彼得堡的地鐵車廂中手持盛載著稀釋漂白水的水樽，走到「擘腿坐」的目標人物身前，亳不猶豫向其胯下傾倒稀釋漂白水。</span>影片中不少男士都中招，有人慌忙撥開多夫加柳克的水樽；有人合腳側身躲避；亦有人似反應不來只是看著她傾倒液體。<br />\n<br />\n多夫加柳克稱所用的漂白水，比家用漂白水劑量濃縮30倍，能輕易使衣物褪色，留下不能洗去的印記。她說：「我們不只要冷卻男人擘腿坐的意欲，也要在他們身上留下永不磨滅的印記。」她稱要將片段獻給「所有當『男人擘腿坐』是正常的『男性』」，又指自己是代表所有在公共交通工具上「容忍別人展示男子氣慨的人」去出一口氣。<br />\n有網民質疑多夫加柳克是僱用臨時演員或請朋友「造馬」演出，她堅決否認，稱行動「絕對真實」，又指暫時未有被潑的乘客起訴她，認為沒人會只為了這件事報警。<br />\n<br />\n去年底多夫加柳克也曾在聖彼得堡地鐵月台快閃自揭裙底，在眾目睽睽下展示內褲，以控訴當地社會的偷拍裙底行為，並要求當局將偷拍刑事化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180928/large/1538098550_ec02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180928%2Flarge%2F1538098550_ec02.jpg&h=4923eb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538033904_4375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F1538033904_4375.jpg&h=c3efe52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180928/58728314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180928%2F58728314&d=pcw7TIdDTT%2FzdYOADSDNsm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1f4f20aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180928%2F58728314&h=e8988322\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180928/58728314</a>"},{"pid":"c865b08c916378179178f1161846ee8baaf4cc11","tid":839650,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"24956692029956c36d924bbb4e46959b9dfe1489","tid":839650,"uid":25240,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c865b08c916378179178f1161846ee8baaf4cc11","tid":839650,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"唔用鏹水淋呢d 推崇沙文主義既父權狗算佢地好彩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9808908d77ad661815d0f9d0a9232009fd148b44","tid":839650,"uid":85965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"肯撚定係搵老臨拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c4809ec751e82666f4fa6897815323e41d624f","tid":839650,"uid":97059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T05:57:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T77frLL_bsg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT77frLL_bsg&d=pcw7TIdDTT%2FzdYOADSDNsm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9d4ac364\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T77frLL_bsg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fb7ed763d2acf5be39d77d9e067b65cf4ffe3d","tid":839650,"uid":1531,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:00:06.000Z","msg":"唔係話平權架咩<br />\n<br />\n你女人就要多廁所<br />\n<br />\n我天生大隻d 有碌鳩頂住就要比你淋？"},{"pid":"e14bd3c878a6b44c22d8f280adb5cec5c8484d17","tid":839650,"uid":50506,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"你話真